Organic Pads & Production

Why Choose Organic?

  • Free from harmful chemicals and synthetic materials
  • Better for sensitive skin and reducing irritation
  • Environmentally friendly production process
  • Biodegradable and sustainable

Top Organic Brands

  • 100% natural bamboo fiber

{/* Natural Remedies Section */}

Natural Remedies

For Cramps

  • Warm compress application
  • Ginger tea with honey
  • Gentle yoga poses
  • Ayurvedic herbs and supplements

For Back Pain

  • Massage with sesame oil
  • Heat therapy
  • Stretching exercises
  • Herbal pain relief remedies
{/* Blood Color Guide Section */}

Blood Color & Health Guide

Bright Red

Fresh, normal menstrual blood. Common at the beginning of your period.

Dark Red/Brown

Older blood that took longer to leave the uterus. Normal, especially at the end of your period.

Pink

Could indicate low estrogen levels. If persistent, consult a healthcare provider.

Orange/Gray

Might indicate infection - consult a healthcare provider if you notice this color.

Clots

Small clots are normal. Large or frequent clots might need medical attention.
